### Test User Management API for error handling, authentication, and logging middleware.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5164



### Test: Get all users (valid token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer your-secret-token

### Test: Get all users (invalid token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer invalid-token

